sentences: Auliʻi Cravalho (; born November 22, 2000) is an American actress and singer who made her acting debut as the titular character in the 2016 Disney 3D computer-animated musical feature film Moana.
Auliʻi Cravalho (; born November 22, 2000) is an American actress and singer who made her acting debut as the titular character in the 2016 Disney 3D computer-animated musical feature film Moana.
She went on to star in the NBC drama series Rise (2018) and the Netflix drama film All Together Now (2020).
